org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml

Class MXMLDialect2009

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect
      • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect2006
        • org.apache.flex.compiler.internal.mxml.MXMLDialect2009
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    MXMLDialect2012

    public class MXMLDialect2009
extends MXMLDialect2006
    This singleton class represents the 2009 dialect of MXML, with the language namespace "http://ns.adobe.com/mxml/2009".

    In addition to the special language tags of the 2006 dialect, this dialect supports <Declarations>, <Definition>, <Library>, <Private>, and <Reparent>.
